<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_1000449> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "epithelial cell of nephron" .
<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CL_1000449> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> "https://cellxgene.cziscience.com/cellguide/CL_1000449" .
