_:B49bb2030b370c6eaf790caee9d726851 <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Axiom> .
_:B49bb2030b370c6eaf790caee9d726851 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#annotatedSource> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/UBERON_0001062> .
